# 10. Shared Memory Layer

Agents need **context sharing**.

Example memory file:

```
memory/project_state.json
```

Example content

```json
{
  "data_cleaned": true,
  "features_created": true,
  "models_trained": ["rf", "xgb"],
  "best_model": "xgb"
}
```

Agents read and update this.

